data.description: This Beautiful 3 bedroom villa now available in this sought-after, low maintenance, gated Edmond community.  Move in ready: new roof, upgraded Fisher & Paykel dishwasher, washer, dryer and refrigerator/freezer included.  Just bring your furnishings, toothbrush and suitcase as you decide how to spend your leisure living. Enjoy a fireside chat surrounded by luxurious designer window coverings in dining area and owner suite, a cocktail on the private patio watching the sun set, a good book from the shelves of the custom built bookcases in the study/bedroom or step outside for a brisk walk on the trails or a workout at the community center.  No doubt you will have lots of company since this development is so conveniently located, only minutes from the turnpike, schools and shopping. Make your move now! Inspections were done and minor repairs completed. This house is ready for you!
